    "description": "Welcome to the world of Datchi, a world where every moment is survival of the fittest! In the land of Phonea the time has come once again for the King Datchi Tournament. A competition ruthless as it is prestigious. A landscape where decimation of your opponent is the only goal. It is now your time to compete and become the King Datchi!<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326380/extras/2bf0aa3610f6a5c90ea73862c6c2b814.poster.avif?t=1730315163\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326380/extras/2bf0aa3610f6a5c90ea73862c6c2b814.webm?t=1730315163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>King Datchi brings consequences to the creature collecting genre.</strong> <br>*Datchi lost in battle are lost forever, any move could be your Datchi's last.<br>*Use ringtones to steal other trainers Datchi but beware the same can be done to you. <br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326380/extras/fc6da47adeffd20d0b162ee7dca6f564.poster.avif?t=1730315163\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326380/extras/fc6da47adeffd20d0b162ee7dca6f564.webm?t=1730315163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326380/extras/fc6da47adeffd20d0b162ee7dca6f564.mp4?t=1730315163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The world of Datchi is not infinite.</strong><br>*Datchi species can go extinct from over hunting, but rarer Datchi become more valuable.<br>*Destroying habitats also effects populations<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326380/extras/01bac760131f36e23a2ac554fd0e206c.poster.avif?t=1730315163\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326380/extras/01bac760131f36e23a2ac554fd0e206c.webm?t=1730315163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>There is no game over</strong><br>Losing your Datchi does not mean losing the game. There are plenty of ways to try again.<br>*Get money working at a part time job to buy a new Datchi and enter the tournament again.<br>*Earn the corpses of rival trainers and sell them on a fluctuating market.<br>*Or catch and sell live Datchi to earn money.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326380/extras/329f6e3fb85d8fed900ffe11248ecad8.poster.avif?t=1730315163\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326380/extras/329f6e3fb85d8fed900ffe11248ecad8.webm?t=1730315163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>A Tournament of the Best</strong><br>*Challenge gyms and other trainers along the way.<br>*Losing and winning affect your rank, only a rank below can challenge a rank above.<br><br><br>Will you be able to rise to the top and become the King Datchi? Or will you only leave a wake of tombstones behind you?<br><br>Also, play snake!",
